Subject to the terms and conditions of this license, you are hereby granted a
worldwide, royalty-free, non-exclusive license to:

  (a) USE the Software on Authorized Systems for personal, educational,
      research, or commercial security hardening purposes;

  (b) COPY and DISTRIBUTE verbatim copies of the Software, provided that you
      retain all copyright notices, this license, and all disclaimer text;

  (c) MODIFY the Software and create Derivative Works, provided that:
        i.  Modified files carry prominent notices stating that you changed them
            and the date of the change;
       ii.  Any Derivative Work you distribute is licensed under this license
            or a license with equivalent or stronger ethical use restrictions;
      iii.  You do not remove, obscure, or alter any Alpha/Beta/Experimental
            stability warnings present in the Software;

  (d) USE the Software in commercial environments, including managed security
      services, provided you comply with all other terms of this license;

  (e) STUDY the Software for educational or research purposes, including
      publication of findings, with appropriate attribution.

